com.g6pay.constants
Class G6Params

java.lang.Object
  com.g6pay.constants.G6Params

public class G6Params
extends java.lang.Object

Constants for the G6Pay platform. Android Manifest params are prefixed with ANDROID_MANIFEST_ HTTP params are prefixed with G6_PARAM_ G6 API URLs are prefixed with G6_API_URL_

Author:
"Peter Hsu"
